        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 31–38. Pyropteron Biology. 31–34. Pyropteron erodiiphaga, (31) male, reared, (32) larva in root of Erodium arborescens, (33) habitat with host plant Erodium arborescens, Tunisia, Djerba (images Friedhelm Mai), (34) male, Morocco, Middle Alas, Col du Zad. 35. Pyropteron affinis, male, Austria, Tirol, Zirl (images FP). 36–38. Pyropteron meriaeformis, (36) habitat with host plant Rumex acetosella, France, Corsica, Ghisonaccia (image DB), (37) male, reared, Portugal, Guarda, Pinzio (image Zdeněk Laštůvka), (38) female, old specimen, France, Corsica, Ghisonaccia (image DB)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4771839/files/figure.png" .

